com.adobe.pdfg.exception

Class ErrorCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.pdfg.exception.ErrorCode

  • public class ErrorCode
extends Object
    Author:
    cahaverl This class defines constants for to use in code when error numbers are needed. Property names are derived from these fields programmatically as described in the comment to getIntegerToPropertyNameMap() below. The strings themselves are defined in ErrorCode.properties and its localizations. The goal here is to have readable code and readable property files, but still be able to pass convenient integers around as error codes.
